{"title":"A First Look at Sim Works’ New Doppo Locust Touring Bike and SimLoaders Bags","link":"https://theradavist.com/sim-works-doppo-locust-touring-bike-and-simloaders-bags/","date":1703077237000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1706\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/Locust1-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/Locust1-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/Locust1-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/Locust1-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/Locust1-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/Locust1-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/Locust1-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/Locust1-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/Locust1-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/Locust1-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><em>We got our first look at the made in Portland, Oregon <a href=\"https://sim-works.com\" target=\"_blank\">Sim Works SimLoaders bags</a> during our <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/chris-king-open-house-2023/\" target=\"_blank\">Chris King Open House Reportage</a> this year and today, the Japanese brand announced the full lineup, coinciding with a completely redesigned Doppo touring bike, now dubbed the Locust and with either 27.5×2.8″ or 29×2.4″ tire clearance!</em></p>\n<p><em>We first <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/makotos-doppo-sim-works-tourer/\" target=\"_blank\">showcased the Doppo</a> when John did <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/riding-circles-around-mount-fuji/\" target=\"_blank\">a bike tour around Mt. Fuji</a> with the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/shaping-cycling-culture-in-nagoya-with-circles-japan/\" target=\"_blank\">Circles crew back in 2016</a>, so it’s exciting to see the newest permutation of this line. Read on for a complete look at the SimLoaders Bags and the new <a href=\"https://www.sim.works/products/doppo-locust-frame-fork-set\" target=\"_blank\">Doppo Locust</a> below!</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03100-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03100-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03100-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03100-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03100-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03100-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03100-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03100-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03100-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03100-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7003.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7003.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7003.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7003.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7003.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7003.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7003.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7003.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7003.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03216-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03216-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03216-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03216-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03216-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03216-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03216-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03216-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03216-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03216-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03033-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03033-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03033-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03033-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03033-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03033-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03033-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03033-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03033-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03033-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.sim.works/products/voyageur-handlebar-bag\" target=\"_blank\">‘Voyageur’ Handlebar bag</a> $248 USD</h3>\n<p>SimWorks’ new mid-capacity modern handlebar mounted carrier for cyclists packing modestly for a long-day adventure, or a light overnighter. An expandable bag flap offers additional coverage and capacity for riders looking to push the volume limits of the bag, while daisy chains on the top and underside of the bag offer the ability to supplement the overall carrying capacity. Constructed of EcoPak exterior material, the bag is lined with nylon for weather resistance.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03221-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03221-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03221-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03221-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03221-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03221-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03221-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03221-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03221-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03221-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03214-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03214-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03214-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03214-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03214-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03214-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03214-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03214-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03214-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03214-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Side accessory pockets with buckle secured covers isolate some compact essentials for quick at hand access. A removable HDPE board insert helps the bag keep it’s bottom shape, while the lining closes via a cinch-top. A midline compression strap helps to draw the front of the bag toward the handlebar mount- which is fiberglass rod reinforced and double stitched. Included are a cinch cord to secure the rear daisy chain to your bikes head tube/stack, as well as (2x) 6″ Voile Straps for handlebar attachment.</p>\n<p><strong>Dimensions:</strong></p>\n<p>Width – 15”<br />\nLength – 6”<br />\nHeight -8”<br />\nLiters – 12</p>\n<p><strong>Materials:</strong></p>\n<p>External fabric – EPX200 EcoPak<br />\nLiner – Waterproof 400D Nylon<br />\nWebbing – Nylon<br />\nBuckles – Duraflex<br />\nRigid support – HDPE plastic<br />\nSupport rods – Fiberglass rods<br />\nMade in Portland, OR</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7025.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7025.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7025.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7025.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7025.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7025.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7025.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7025.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7025.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6939.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6939.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6939.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6939.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6939.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6939.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6939.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6939.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6939.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.sim.works/products/chrysalis-saddle-bag\" target=\"_blank\">‘Chrysalis’ Saddle Bag</a> $160 USD</h3>\n<p>Striking a sweet spot between our En-Route compact saddle bag, and long-haul loaders you might find from other manufacturers is our ‘Chrysalis’ saddle bag. While offering enough space to pack some layers or even a lightweight bivy or sleeping quilt- the bag’s modest size serves as a worthy supplement to a frame bag, handlebar bag, or fork mounted cargo carrying solution while minimizing that jutting tail from hanging out behind your saddle.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7002.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7002.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7002.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7002.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7002.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7002.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7002.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7002.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF7002.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Constructed from the same EcoPak as the other bags in our Sim Loader line, the ‘Chrysalis’ pack utilizes a roll-style buckle closure and a separate buckle and strap system to secure the pack to your saddle. The attachment point at your seat post is achieved through opposing micro D-rings to anchor an included 6″ Voile strap. Neoprene against your seatpost and saddle rails, and a waterproof nylon liner round out durability and range of environmental considerations. A reflective band on the top and underside of the bag provides a dose of safety for riders out after dark.</p>\n<p><strong>Dimensions:</strong></p>\n<p>Width – 5”<br />\nLength – 5”<br />\nHeight -14”<br />\nLiters – Up to 6.5</p>\n<p><strong>Materials:</strong></p>\n<p>External fabric – EPX200 EcoPak<br />\nLiner – Waterproof 400D Nylon<br />\nWebbing – Nylon<br />\nBuckles – Duraflex<br />\nReflective tape<br />\nCoverlight Neoprene (tarp material for abrasion and slip resistance)<br />\nMade in Portland, OR</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6958.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6958.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6958.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6958.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6958.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6958.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6958.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6958.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6958.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6993.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6993.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6993.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6993.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6993.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6993.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6993.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6993.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6993.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.sim.works/products/en-route-saddle-bag\" target=\"_blank\">‘En-Route’ compact saddle Bag</a> $70 USD</h3>\n<p>A minimal but practical roll-top style saddle bag to bring along some essentials on your ride. Enough capacity for some tools, a lightweight layer, EDC items or some food. Reinforced at high stress points, and includes a reflective strip on both the top and underside of the bag. Lined with nylon, En-route closes with a roll-style buckle to keep the elements out. Daisy chain nylon webbing provides an attachment point to lash an included 6″ Voile strap to your seatpost, and an additional 15″ included Voile strap around the bag and your saddle rails. Coverlight Neoprene adds a layer of abrasion and slip resistance to a list of features. Lightweight, waterproof, durable and at home on an endless range of bikes for making sure you don’t leave home or the trail head without your essentials.</p>\n<p><strong>Dimensions:</strong></p>\n<p>Width – 3.5”<br />\nLength – 3.5”<br />\nHeight – 11”<br />\nCapacity -Up to 2.5L</p>\n<p><strong>Materials:</strong></p>\n<p>External fabric – EPX200 EcoPak<br />\nLiner – Waterproof 400D Nylon<br />\nWebbing – Nylon<br />\nBuckles – Duraflex<br />\nReflective Tape<br />\nCoverlight Neoprene (tarp material for abrasion and slip resistance)<br />\nMade in Portland, OR</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6950.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6950.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6950.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6950.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6950.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6950.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6950.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6950.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSCF6950.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03240-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03240-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03240-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03240-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03240-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03240-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03240-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03240-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03240-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03240-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w