/12/SIMWORKS-DOPPO-Locust17-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/SIMWORKS-DOPPO-Locust17-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1367&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1709\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/SIMWORKS-DOPPO-Locust15-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/SIMWORKS-DOPPO-Locust15-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/SIMWORKS-DOPPO-Locust15-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,684&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/SIMWORKS-DOPPO-Locust15-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1335&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/SIMWORKS-DOPPO-Locust15-scaled.jpg?resize=768,513&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/SIMWORKS-DOPPO-Locust15-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1201&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/SIMWORKS-DOPPO-Locust15-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,891&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/SIMWORKS-DOPPO-Locust15-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/SIMWORKS-DOPPO-Locust15-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/SIMWORKS-DOPPO-Locust15-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1367&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Most of a locust’s life is spent in solitude, yet at a specific phase in its life cycle; it will swarm en masse, traveling across open landscapes in search of food, but only after abundant rainfall when vegetative growth is abundant. While they are often depicted as villainous and gregarious insects, they are keystones in a healthy ecological system. Like the natural cycle of all things, locusts play an important role in arid steppe landscapes: controlling fire fuel!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"694\" src=\"https:/