t.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03182-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC03182-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Locusts are incredibly resilient in all terrains, making them a beautiful and misunderstood inspiration for the next stage of the Doppo, sometimes solitary, sometimes with friends.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08407-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08407-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08407-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08407-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08407-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08407-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08407-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08407-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08407-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08407-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08738-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08738-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08738-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08738-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08738-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08738-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08738-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08738-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08738-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/12/DSC08738-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><em>The Doppo Locust is the first Doppo designed around a 120 mm travel suspension fork with a suspension-corrected segmented fork.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Size : M , L , XL</li>\n<li>Made in Japan</li>\n<li>Frame : Chromoly Tube（Tange no.3）</li>\n<li>Fork : Doppo Original MTB（Offset 47mm / Lenght 465mm）</li>\n<li>Head Size : Top ZS 44mm , Bottom EC 44mm</li>\n<li>Brake Style : Front : IS Mount , Rear : Post 160mm mount</li>\n<li>Max Tire Clearance : 27.5×2.8″ , 29×2.4″</li>\n<li>Front Wheel Fix : 110x15mm Thru Axle</li>\n<li>Rear Wheel Fix : 148x12mm Thru Axle</li>\n<li>BB Shell : 73mm BSA Threaded</li>\n<li>Component : MTB</li>\n<li>Seat Post Clamp: 35mm</li>\n<li>Seatpost Diameter: 30.9mm</li>\n<li>Bottle Cage Mount :２</li>\n<li>Cargo Cage Mount : 3（Fork x2 , Under The Down Tube x1）</li>\n<li>Dropper Post Compatible : Stealth Dropper Port on Seat Tube</li>\n<li>Recommend Suspension Stroke : 120mm</li>\n<li>Color: Cosmic Lavender</li>\n<li>Price: $1880 with flat shipping at $100</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Check out the complete new drop at <a href=\"https://www.sim.works/\" target=\"_blank\">Sim Works</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/sim-works-doppo-locust-touring-bike-and-simloaders-bags/\">A First Look at Sim Works’ New Doppo Locust Touring Bike and SimLoaders Bags</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"f3881ab98b8bd72c2cd7114ad9a81f3c0bac9a5f0606357dc12747e8af27071c","category":"Cycling"}